** '''Chancellor Hassan:''' Well... we do currently have a very urgent issue we need to resolve, and I suppose you look like someone who knows how to get a job done. Are you definitely interested in helping?
** {{tselect|Start the Prince Ali Rescue quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' Of course.
*** '''Chancellor Hassan:''' You'll find our Spymaster, Osman, just outside the palace. Go to him and tell him I sent you. He will fill you in on the details of our problem.
*** '''Player:''' Alright, I'll get to it.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
